Now give me next week home workout plan for him, copy paste format again. If the person is following the the split for a month, make a new split or him and increase intensity, if they are following single body part, push it to 2 body parts, if following 2 body parts, change to 3. If following 3 body parts a day, push to 4. And if already following 4 body parts a day, start cycle again with single body part per day. Make sure the time taken to workout is similar to usual, keep volume similar of the workout, but increase by 15% if completed a month.
